CustomField.description: The message id of this email on the sending user's email service. This field is used to create a link to the email message in the browser.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: The message id of this email on the sending user's email service (according ti the rfc822 header field "message-id"). This field is used to create a link to the email message in the browser.
CustomField.label: Email Message Id
